						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the shrine of Rāma.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1687, Krōdhana, Phālguṇa śu. 7.</hi> However, the Śaka and cyclic years do not tally.</p>						

						<p>It records the grant of a land as <hi rend="italic">nētravaṭu-mānyam</hi> and of a garden made by <hi rend="italic">reḍḍi</hi> and <hi rend="italic">karnaṇam</hi> of Gaṅganapalle to <hi rend="italic">sāḷvu-pakshi dommari</hi> Veṅkaṭa-reḍḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
